name: We destroyed our world#2
description:
The verdure is fading away. Colors are splashed on the canvas in disarray only to ruin the natural masterpiece.    
the stream is not limpid any more. No longer does the river join the sea; No, it’s running in vain after the dark filthy footsteps of human beings, slowed down by stones and gravels.
This is Mother Earth who is striving to breathe. And a sick mother will leave no heritage to her children but sickness.
The “Incursion” collection is about garbage, and human intrusion in nature.
